DAX query library containing 80 plus verified queries for the Sites and Costs Summary Power BI semantic model. Each query pattern shows the exact DAX syntax with correct measure names table names and filter values. The agent should select the matching query pattern and substitute the user requested filter values before sending to the Power BI tool. Covers active facilities, NBV, asset registers, ROU, contracts, PSL facilities, facility types, operating expenses, expense categories, and risk summaries with filters by region country city PSL hemisphere and status.
